  <summary date="2022-03-08T21:58:04Z" status="Introduced in Senate">American Grown Act

This bill prohibits certain agencies from procuring cut flowers or cut greens grown outside the United States. The bill also sets forth requirements for such agencies accepting gifts of cut flowers or cut greens grown outside the United States.</summary>
